abstract: Jimmy Mullen and Paul Dunne make professional debuts at Alfred Dunhill Links Championship; both shoot eight-under-par 64 in first round and share lead with Kristoffer Broberg.
lead_paragraph: Jimmy Mullen and Paul Dunne, in their professional debuts, each shot an eight-under-par 64 to share the lead with Kristoffer Broberg after the first round of the Alfred Dunhill Links Championship in Scotland.

headline.main: In Debuts, Sharing Lead in Scotland
